# $Header: $

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +metadata.xml:
  Add minimal metadata.xml(s) for QA.

  09 Sep 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  Update ebuild file format from "# $Header: $" to "# $Id"

   Since Gentoo changes the VCS from CVS to git, ebuild header is changed.

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  media-fonts/{noto*,source-han-sans*}: Modify ${DOCs} to list from array.

    font.eclass supports space-delimited listed ${DOCS} only,
   though EAPI(>=4) can treat arrayed ${DOCS}.
    Therefore, space-delimited list (not array) makes codes shorter,
   because src_install can be left as default spec of font.eclass.

  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  Update for version 1.004.

    About version 1.004,
   see https://github.com/googlei18n/noto-cjk/blob/master/NEWS

  30 May 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  Update to EAPI=5 and git-r3.eclass

*noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999 (27 Jan 2015)

  27 Jan 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> +noto-sans-cjk-jp-9999.ebuild:
  Commit for initializing, Move from GitHub

